     - Barcode or EANNumber.
     - Department in which the regulation must be made
     - Quantity. Must not be 0
     - Costprice. If 0 - use what is on item
     - salesprice. Ignores this one for now - will always use the one from item, sinse this is the one used when doing a sale.

     Must do:

      - Fetch item and all information about item
      - Insert label
  */

