'This table contains information about turnover.
There will always be turnover summarized by both payment and group.
But only one may be used to create financial records.';

COMMENT ON TABLE CLOSE_DAY_CUSTOMERDEPOSIT IS
'This table will hold information about customers deposit and have they where paid.
Usually this will result in a financial record type D.
But some customer wants to have a financial record of type F, which is why the payment and the payments account number and external vat code are present';

COMMENT ON TABLE CLOSE_DAY_CUSTOMERSALE IS
'This table will contain all customer sale made on credit (Debitorsalg)';

